      "text": "7. Jo tee irr wairojschees/\ntee prett manni irr apgreh\nſchees. Es pahrwehrtiſchu w\nno Gohdu par Raunu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": null,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta IV. Nodalla.\nCluddinaſchanas tahs Sohdibas pahr teem\nIſraela Laudim ſawo Grehku-deht: 1. Ar\nweenu Draudeſchanu tahs paſchas: 2. Un\nweenu peetiſigu Mahziſchanu uhs Jubdu/\nka tam buhs no tahdas jargatees : 15.\n"
