    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Tee ehd tohs Greh-\nmanno Lauschu/ un ilgojahs\nweens ar ſawu Dwehſeli p\nwinno Noseegumeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "1. Laufait ta KUNGA\nWahrdiu juhs Iſraela\nBehrni/ jo tam KUN-\nGAM irr weena Sohda Leeta\nar teem Semmes Eedſihwota-\njeem/ tapehz ka nekahda Peetiſ-\nziba/ nedg Labdarriſchana/ nedg\nDrewa Atſihſchana eekſch tahs\nSemmes irraid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Tadeht buhs tas Pree-\nris täpatt ka tee Landidis / un\npeemekleſchu pahr winnu win-\nZettus/ un atmaſſachu winnu\nſawus Darbus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "2. Bet Lahdetchana/ un Mel-\nli/ un Slepkawiba/ un Sahdst-\nba/ un Laufibas-Pahrkahpscha-\nna/ tee lauschabs zauri/ un wee-\nna Affins-Waina nahks pakkat\nohtru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Un tee ehdihs/ bet ne p\nehdis/ tee mankoſs/ bet tas tee\nne tsdohſees/ tapehz ka tee\nKUNGU irr atſtahjuſchi /\nwinnu ne zeeniſſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "3. Tadeht behdajahs ta Sem-\nine/ un wiſs / kas eeſch tahs\ndsihwo/ waidehs ar teem Sweh-\nreem Lanka/ un ar teem Put-\nneem appakſch Debbes / ir tahs\nJuhnas Siwis taps atrautas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Manziba/ un Wihn\nun jauns Wihs atjemi\nSirzi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Tomehr laid netweens bar-\nrahs/ nedg jevkahdu pahrmahza/\njo tatvi Landidis irr ka tee/ kas ar\nto Preeſteri barrahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Manni Landidis waiza\nwu Kohfu / un winna Spee-\nbuhs teem ſinaamn darriht /\ntas Manzibas Garb peew-\ntohs/ ka tee prett ſawu Dee-\nManzibu dſenn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Tadeht krittiſi tu Deena/\nir tas patg Praiveets krittihs ar\n"
